  - Automatically Rebuild Your Search Index: Enable automatic index rebuilds to ensure customers view up-to-date product information.
  - Get Improved Page Performance with Displayable Product Fields (Beta): Configure displayable product fields for improved store performance and page load times.
  - Sort Products by SKU: Remove Product SKU as a default sortable field on search and category pages in D2C stores. 
  - Improve Your Browse Experience with the Redesigned Product List Page: Redesign sort options, filter selections, and accordion dropdown menus on the product list page.
